name: Part One: I Heard Of A Place (In The Meantime Short Film)

metadata.name: Part One: I Heard Of A Place (In The Meantime Short Film) 1
metadata.description:
IN THE MEANTIME is a three-part short film that touches on surveillance, therapy, & the lengths one will go through to find peace. "I Heard Of A Place" is the first part. 

The whole film will serve as a prelude to Heno.'s highly anticipated project "I'm Tired of Being Hypersurveilled". 

5% of all Heno.'s 2023 sales will be going directly to social impact organizations.
